quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  76,23,Chisimu Uwwe tujitulwisye kukwenu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) Qur’an kujitulusya kwapanandi panandi (kuti n'jisunje chenene)
  76,24,Basi pililani ni lilamusi lya Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) ni ngasimumpikanila mwa ŵanganyao jwasambi kapena jwakanila (jwalijose)
  76,25,"Soni likumbuchilani lina lya Ambuje ŵenu kundaŵi ni kwigulo (pakuswali swala sya Fajr, Dhuhr ni Asr)"
  76,26,"Soni chilo munsujudilani (pakuswali swala sya Maghrib ni Isha), ni munswejesyeje chilo ndema jelewu"
  76,27,"Chisimu ŵanganyaŵa akunonyelwa umi wachitema (wa duniya), ni akulileka munyuma mwao Lisiku lya usito"
  76,28,"Uwwe ni ŵatwaagumbile ŵanganyao soni twaliyiye kagumbidwe kao, soni tuli tusachile mpaka tuiche nao ŵane ŵanti mpela ŵanganyao kwinjila m’malo mwao (nambo ali ŵakun'jogopa Allah)"
  76,29,"Chisimu galakwe (ma Ȃyaga) gaŵele chikumbusyo, basi jwaakusaka aliikolochesye chilepe litala lyakuujila kwa M'bujegwe (Allah)"
  76,30,"Ni nganim'ba nsachile ŵanganyammwe ikaŵeje akasache kaje Allah, chisimu Allah aŵele Jwakumanyilila nnope, Jwalunda lwakusokoka"
  76,31,"Taakan'jinjisye jwansachile ku ukoto Wakwe (ku Mbepo), nambo ŵakulitenda lupuso ŵalinganyichisye ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope"